Package: guide
Title: A simple way to add, change or update your file or drectory
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person("JP", "Monteagudo",
    email = "jpmonteagudo2014@gmail.com", 
    role = c("aut", "cre","cph"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0009-0003-6465-6658"))
Maintainer: The package maintainer <jpmonteagudo2014@gmail.com>
Description: Point R to a file's relative path within your project with 'guide_to_file'.
    Use the 'guide_to_parent' function to move up any number of levels within your project.
    Use the `guide_to_child` function to move down to a specified directory or to create a new directory.
